{"_id":"7gDYQnedOa5FnoJ8","name":"Cantrips","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>Blue mages learn a number of cantrips, or 0-<wbr />level spells. These spells are cast like any other spell, but they do not consume MP and may be used again. Blue mages begin with 4 0-<wbr />level spells and gain an additional 0-<wbr />level spell every three levels after 1st level.</p>\n<p><a style=\"text-shadow: red 0px 0px 8px;\" href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#cantrips\">Link to Cantrips on FFd20</a></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","max":0},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Blue Mage"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":null},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":null,"damage":null,"damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save"