{"_id":"C2Xxp3esmX1ik2uE","name":"Azure Talent, Adv: Intel","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Prerequisite: </strong>Libra class feature</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Whenever the blue mage uses the Libra ability, he may add one of these two effects:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Libra affects all creatures in a 60-foot-radius centered on the blue mage</li>\n<li>the effects of Libra remain for a number of rounds equal to the blue mage&rsquo;s Intelligence modifier.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This talent may be taken twice. If taken a second time, the blue mage gains both abilities.&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff6400; text-decoration-line: underline;\">Link to Azure Talents on FFd20</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Advanced Azure Talent"]],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","max":0},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Blue Mage"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"cou