{"_id":"FXVuNSTVB8NUsHjB","name":"Azure Talent: Field of Study: Adroitness","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><strong>Prerequisite(s): Analysis class feature</strong></p>\n<hr />\n<p><br />The blue mage with this talent adds this ability to her list of Analysis abilities. The blue mage learns how to better manipulate magic so to be more effective against creatures of that race, and informs her allies on how to do so, granting her allies a +1 bonus on caster level checks to overcome spell resistance made against them. If the blue mage succeeds on her Knowledge check by 5 or more, then this bonus increases to +2. If the blue mage succeeds on her Knowledge check by 10 or more, then this bonus increases to +3. If the blue mage succeeds on her Knowledge check by 20 or more, then this bonus increases to +4.</p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #ff6400; text-decoration-line: underline;\">Link to Azure Talents on FFd20</span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[["Azure Talent"]],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","max":0},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Blue Mage"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"su","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","override