{"_id":"MUK2HW3Gv14u9gAk","name":"Azure Talents","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","system":{"description":{"value":"<p class=\"western\">As a blue mage gains experience, she learns a number of talents that assist her in manipulating spells and other forms of magic. At 2nd level and every two levels thereafter, a blue mage gains one azure talent. A blue mage cannot select an individual talent more than once. Talents marked with an asterisk add effects to a blue mage&rsquo;s spellcasting ability. Only one of these talents can be applied to an individual spell and the decision must be made before the spell is cast.</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.MJ8i7adpo1awE2WK]{Azure Talent: Arcane Fighter}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.JlHcf6yhARbM4IUP]{Azure Talent: Arcane Pool}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.MwTGJztLjDqxLxj6]{Azure Talent: Broad Analysis}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.z3wlpasYIuZYECIz]{Azure Talent: Concentrate}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.Fb7CGbciYjQwfmeH]{Azure Talent: Detect Traps}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.wkcy71E7VcetesG4]{Azure Talent: Empowered Magic}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.gpQMlnBtfDTD6n1e]{Azure Talent: Familiar}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.FXVuNSTVB8NUsHjB]{Azure Talent: Field of Study: Adroitness}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.r4lZcFQ30rci5MKE]{Azure Talent: Field of Study: Torpefy}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.7ZMplCgwY8IeslaU]{Azure Talent: Focused Analysis}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.Bvmwkwgo6DqicojU]{Azure Talent: Improved Scan}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.crvLCKCIShtMQoiZ]{Azure Talent: Mage Accuracy*}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.YRmnIrRqyOToCo0o]{Azure Talent: Mage Training}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.0RLxrYh81ubo48zz]{Azure Talent: Silent Magic}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.xJnUqsdmfWrhj5s9]{Azure Talent: Spell Guard*}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.bu1geCP2wsUKlsk7]{Azure Talent: Spell Restraint*}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.44kF2n9uxKSDkDUi]{Azure Talent: Still Magic}</p>\n<p>@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.KAiKqr83xQ5OxEFh]{Azure Talent: Surecast}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of azure talents can be found here: <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/azure-talents/\">Azure Talents</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"western\">At 12th, and every two levels thereafter, a blue mage learns further talents to assist her in manipulating spells and other forms of magic. She may choose one of the following advanced azure talents in place of an azure talent. Talents marked with an asterisk add effects to a blue mage&rsquo;s spellcasting ability. Only one of these talents can be applied to an individual spell and the decision must be made before the spell is cast.</p>\n<p class=\"western\">@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.RK43gr6h2K26MxqS]{Azure Talent, Adv: Greater Weakening Gaze}</p>\n<p class=\"western\">@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.nLV90tRP6PyiWfld]{Azure Talent, Adv: Improved Azure Counter}</p>\n<p class=\"western\">@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.nssJZOMFYisRCViE]{Azure Talent, Adv: Improved Weakening Gaze}</p>\n<p class=\"western\">@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.C2Xxp3esmX1ik2uE]{Azure Talent, Adv: Intel}</p>\n<p class=\"western\">@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.n8fUo1mkR2VeB8TB]{Azure Talent, Adv: Mage Focus*}</p>\n<p class=\"western\">@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.GxXxEoX0K0MQZgoh]{Azure Talent, Adv: Maximized Magic}</p>\n<p class=\"western\">@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.NLxBFl8lg1psW5QQ]{Azure Talent, Adv: Quick Check}</p>\n<p class=\"western\">@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.VaSbOPcX9sksVUpt]{Azure Talent, Adv: Quickened Magic}</p>\n<p class=\"western\">@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.jnLtF9BxTHfBu6On]{Azure Talent, Adv: Spell Diligence*}</p>\n<p class=\"western\">@Compendium[ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.ZtT5YptoIrABiRpr]{Azure Talent, Adv: Weakening Gaze}</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of advanced azure talents can be found here: <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/azure-talents/#advanced-azure-talents\">Advanced Azure Talents</a></li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","max":0},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Blue Mage"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"none","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customC