{"name":"Blue Mage","type":"class","img":"modules/ffd20-content/assets/classes/Blue_Mage.png","_id":"W5HM5nKsx1UaBalb","system":{"description":{"value":"<p><em>The blue mages, warrior-<wbr />mages who master the techniques of monsters, comprise an organization called the Azure Academy. Their motto is &ldquo;fight fire with fire.&rdquo; When not performing undercover missions, or adventuring in an area where doing so would endanger them unnecessarily, they prefer to wear blue&mdash;they claim that this is the color of monsters&rsquo; souls. Blue mages are invariably those who have had close calls with monsters and learned from them, intuitively figuring out how to predict, evade, and finally replicate monsters&rsquo; attacks. The Azure Academy observes particularly observant adventurers and attempts to recruit the cream of the crop. After training for at least a month at the Academy&rsquo;s headquarters, a new recruit is ready to go out and begin amassing his own arsenal of monster techniques.</em></p>\n<p><strong>Role:</strong> Blue mages has a unique set of skills and spells to provide tactical support over the battleground. Often trying to learn new spells from unique creatures, they aren&rsquo;t afraid to get their hands dirty to acquire new knowledge.</p>\n<p><strong>Alignment:</strong> Any</p>\n<p><strong>Hit Die:</strong> d8</p>\n<p><strong>Starting Wealth:</strong> 4d6 &times; 10 gil (average 140 gil.) In addition, each character begins play with an outfit worth 10 gil or less.</p>\n<p><strong>Class Skills</strong><br />The blue mage&rsquo;s class skills (and the key ability for each skill) are Acrobatics (Dex), Appraise (Int), Craft (Int), Fly (Dex), Knowledge (all) (Int),&nbsp;Linguistics&nbsp;(Int), Profession (Wis), and Spellcraft (Int).</p>\n<p><strong>Skill Points Per Level:</strong> 6 + Int modifier</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/\">Link to Blue Mage on FFd20</a></p>\n<h2 class=\"tablepress-table-name tablepress-table-name-id-24\">Table: Blue Mage</h2>\n<table id=\"tablepress-24\" class=\"tablepress tablepress-id-24 class-magic\" border=\"1\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"5\">\n<thead>\n<tr class=\"row-1\">\n<th class=\"column-1\">Level</th>\n<th class=\"column-6\">Special</th>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">MP</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">Spell Level</td>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr class=\"row-3\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">1st</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#blue-magery\">Blue Magery</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#spell-proficiency\">Spell Proficiency</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#cantrips\">Cantrips</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#limit-breaks\">Limit Breaks</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">3</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1st</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-4\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">2nd</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#scan\">Scan</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#scan\">Azure Talent</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">4</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">1st</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-5\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">3rd</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#armored-mage\">Armored Mage</a> (Light), <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#analysis\">Analysis</a> (Lucubrate)</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">5</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">2nd</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-6\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">4th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#azure-physical-training\">Azure Physical Training</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#scan\">Azure Talent</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">6</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">2nd</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-7\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">5th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#clear-mind\">Clear Mind</a> I, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#blue-magery\">Blue Magery</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#azure-learning\">Azure Learning</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">8</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">3rd</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-8\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">6th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#invoke\">Invoke</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#scan\">Azure Talent</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#refined-knowledge\">Refined Knowledge</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">11</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">3rd</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-9\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">7th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#i-know-that-trick\">I Know That Trick</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#analysis\">Analysis</a> (Mettle)</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">15</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">4th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-10\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">8th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#azure-physical-training\">Azure Physical Training</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#scan\">Azure Talent</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">20</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">4th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-11\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">9th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#blue-magery\">Blue Magery</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#azure-counter\">Azure Counter</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">26</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">5th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-12\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">10th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#clear-mind\">Clear Mind</a> II, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#libra\">Libra</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#scan\">Azure Talent</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">32</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">5th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-13\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">11th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#simulation\">Simulation</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#analysis\">Analysis</a> (Foreknowledge)</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">39</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">6th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-14\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">12th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#improved-invoke\">Improved Invoke</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#azure-physical-training\">Azure Physical Training</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#scan\">Advanced Azure Talent</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">47</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">6th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-15\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">13th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#blue-magery\">Blue Magery</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#easy-learning\">Easy Learning</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">56</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">7th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-16\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">14th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#scan\">Advanced Azure Talent</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">65</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">7th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-17\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">15th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#clear-mind\">Clear Mind</a> III, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#doublecast\">Doublecast</a> (1/day), <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#analysis\">Analysis</a> (Flummox)</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">75</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">8th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-18\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">16th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#azure-physical-training\">Azure Physical Training</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#scan\">Advanced Azure Talent</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">86</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">8th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-19\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">17th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#azure-lore\">Azure Lore</a> (3/day), <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#blue-magery\">Blue Magery</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">98</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">9th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-20\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">18th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#1-mp-spell\">1 MP Spell</a> (3/day), <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#scan\">Advanced Azure Talent</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">110</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">9th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-21\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">19th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#cerulean-focus\">Cerulean Focus</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#analysis\">Analysis</a> (Puissance)</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">122</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">9th</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row-22\">\n<td class=\"column-1\">20th</td>\n<td class=\"column-6\"><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#clear-mind\">Clear Mind</a> IV, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#assimilation\">Assimilation</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#azure-physical-training\">Azure Physical Training</a>, <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#scan\">Advanced Azure Talent</a></td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">135</td>\n<td style=\"text-align: center;\">9th</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<h2 class=\"pagebreak\">Favored Class Bonuses</h2>\n<p>Instead of receiving an additional skill rank or hit point whenever they gain a level in a favored class, some races have the option of choosing from a number of other bonuses, depending upon their favored classes. The following options are available to the listed race who have blue mage as their favored class, and unless otherwise stated, the bonus applies each time you select the listed favored class reward.</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/dwarf/\">Dwarf</a>:</strong>&nbsp;Add +1/4 bonus to damage to the blue mage&rsquo;s natural attacks.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/elvaan/\">Elvaan</a>:</strong>&nbsp;Add +1/6 bonus to Knowledge (all) skill checks.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/galka/\">Galka</a>:</strong>&nbsp;Add +1/4 bonus to damage to the blue mage&rsquo;s natural attacks.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/genome/\">Genome</a>:</strong> Add +1/6 bonus to all Knowledge skill checks.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/half-breed/\">Half-Breed</a>:</strong> Add one spell known from the blue mage spell list. This spell must be at least one level below the highest spell level the blue mage can cast.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/hume/\">Hume</a>:</strong>&nbsp;Add one spell known from the blue mage spell list. This spell must be at least one level below the highest spell level the blue mage can cast.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/beastman-tribes/kojin/\">Kojin</a>:</strong>&nbsp;Add +1/2 to the blue mage&rsquo;s caster level when determining the range of any spells with the water descriptor.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/mithra/\">Mithra</a>:</strong>&nbsp;Add +1/6 bonus to Knowledge (all) skill checks.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/moogle/\">Moogle</a>:</strong> Add +1/4 bonus to damage to the blue mage&rsquo;s natural attacks.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/nu-mou/\">Nu Mou</a>:</strong>&nbsp;Add +1/6 bonus to all Knowledge skill checks.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/qu/\">Qu</a>:</strong>&nbsp;Add +1/6 bonus to Knowledge (all) skill checks.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/ronso/\">Ronso</a>:</strong> Add a +1/2 bonus on concentration checks made to cast defensively.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/core-races/tarutaru/\">Tarutaru</a>:</strong> Add +1/6 bonus to Knowledge (all) skill checks.</li>\n<li><strong><a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/races/base-races/viera/\">Viera</a>:</strong>&nbsp;Add one spell known from the blue mage&rsquo;s spell list. This spell must be at least one level below the highest-<wbr />level spell the blue mage can cast.</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>Archetypes</h2>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<ul>\n<li>A complete list of blue mage archetypes can be found here: <a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/archetypes/\">Blue Mage Archetypes</a></li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"links":{"children":[],"classAssociations":[{"id":"ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.MUK2HW3Gv14u9gAk","dataType":"compendium","name":"Azure Talents","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","level":2,"_index":0},{"id":"ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.8ZtqplIKkXioHARy","dataType":"compendium","name":"Blue Magery","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","level":1,"_index":1},{"id":"ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.T7iWDdiPzI2GSZ6i","dataType":"compendium","name":"Limit Break: Dual Azure Mastery","img":"systems/ffd20/icons/actions/LimitBreak.png","level":1,"_index":2},{"id":"ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.SKm1tNETEmPK6xK4","dataType":"compendium","name":"Limit Break: Scan Master","img":"systems/ffd20/icons/actions/LimitBreak.png","level":1,"_index":3},{"id":"ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.U73jRV2WHuMXQjyE","dataType":"compendium","name":"Spell Proficiency","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","level":1,"_index":4},{"id":"ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.7gDYQnedOa5FnoJ8","dataType":"compendium","name":"Cantrips","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","level":1,"_index":5},{"id":"ffd20-content.ffd20-class-pack-base_blue-mage.JF6HF8JU0NNPoExf","dataType":"compendium","name