{"name":"Armored Mage","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","_id":"azejEnAcb9hmQmga","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 3rd level, normally, <span data-darkreader-inline-color=\"\">armor of any kind interferes with a spell-<wbr />caster&rsquo;s gestures, which can cause spells to fail if those spells have a somatic component. A blue mage&rsquo;s limited focus and specialized training, however, allows her to avoid spell failure so long as she sticks to light armor and light shields. This training does not extend to medium armor or heavy shields. This ability does not apply to spells gained from a different spell-<wbr />casting class.</span></p>\n<p><span data-darkreader-inline-color=\"\"><a style=\"text-shadow: red 0px 0px 8px;\" href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#armored-mage\">Link to Armored Mage on FFd20</a></span></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[],"uses":{"per":null,"value":0,"maxFormula":"","autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","max":0},"attackNotes":[],"effectNotes":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"contextNotes":[],"links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"","useCustomTag":false,"armorProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"weaponProf":{"value":[],"custom":""},"languages":{"value":[],"custom":""},"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"scriptCalls":[],"featType":"classFeat","associations":{"classes":[["Blue Mage"]]},"showInQuickbar":false,"abilityType":"ex","crOffset":"","disabled":false,"classSkills":{},"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":null,"units":""},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"","at