{"name":"Assimilation","type":"feat","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","_id":"lOx6syDcCboWRdv5","system":{"description":{"value":"<p>At 20th level, the blue mage absorb any special qualities from creatures she has used the&nbsp;<em>Libra&nbsp;</em>ability on. As a standard action, usable per day equal to the blue mage&rsquo;s Intelligence modifier, the blue mage may absorb only one special quality from a creature at a time. A creature affected by this ability must make a Fortitude save (DC 10 + half of the blue mage&rsquo;s level + her Intelligence modifier) or temporary loses its special quality ability. The only special quality ability that cannot be absorbed is the creature type. Absorbing a creature&rsquo;s special qualities overrides her own. This ability lasts for a number of rounds equal to 3 + the blue mage&rsquo;s Intelligence modifier. In addition, the blue mage learns the special quality ability and may be reused at any given time with a successful appropriate Knowledge skill check of DC 15 + the CR of the creature that uses up an assimilation ability usage.</p>\n<p><a style=\"text-shadow: red 0px 0px 8px;\" href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/classes/base-classes/blue-mage/#armored-mage\">Link to Armored Mage on FFd20</a></p>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"actions":[{"_id":"4BQGV2SYiYQ4vjjQ","name":"Use","img":"icons/svg/item-bag.svg","description":"","tag":"","activation":{"cost":1,"type":"standard"},"unchainedAction":{"activation":{"cost":1,"type":""}},"duration":{"value":"3+@abilities.int.mod","units":"round"},"target":{"value":""},"range":{"value":null,"units":"","maxIncrements":1,"minValue":null,"minUnits":""},"uses":{"autoDeductCharges":true,"autoDeductChargesCost":"1","self":{"value":0,"maxFormula":"","per":null},"per":"day","value":0,"maxFormula":"@abilities.int.mod","max":0},"measureTemplate":{"type":"","size":"","overrideColor":false,"customColor":"","overrideTexture":false,"customTexture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"save","atta